03:46.929 --> 03:48.631
Chief Pratt
killed himself?

03:48.731 --> 03:50.232
You'd think so,
but no.

03:50.332 --> 03:51.794
Murdered.

03:51.894 --> 03:52.875
What?

03:52.975 --> 03:54.636
Yeah, a couple
of good whacks

03:54.736 --> 03:56.598
at the back of the head.

03:56.698 --> 03:58.700
That's like Nola.

03:59.861 --> 04:01.562
Pratt was protecting somebody

04:01.663 --> 04:04.165
