Yeah.

09:03.859 --> 09:05.321
May I?

09:05.421 --> 09:06.762
Of course.

09:06.862 --> 09:07.843
Thanks.

09:07.943 --> 09:09.965
How's your book
going?

09:10.065 --> 09:11.567
Slowly.

09:11.667 --> 09:15.050
There's a lot of gray areas
to clear up, you know.

09:15.150 --> 09:17.152
[clears throat]

09:18.873 --> 09:21.496
Listen, I wanted to ask you, um,

09:21.596 --> 09:25.339
did your wife ever mention
a compromising note she had

09:25.439 --> 09:27.441
that Harry Quebert wrote?

09:27.841 --> 09:29.143
How did you know
about that?

09:29.243 --> 09:30.504
Well, your wife told me.

09:30.604 --> 09:31.705
She told me,

09:31.805 --> 09:33.066
but then she said
it went missing,

09:33.166 --> 09:34.948
and I... [chuckles]

09:35.048 --> 09:36.870
Look, all due respect,

09:36.970 --> 09:38.151
it's a little hard to know
what to believe

09:38.251 --> 09:40.073
when it comes to, uh...

09:40.173 --> 09:42.875
Believe her, Mr. Goldman.

09:42.975 --> 09:45.197
My wife may not be the sweetest
thing in the world,

09:45.297 --> 09:47.900
but she doesn't lie.

09:55.387 --> 10:02.133
[singing to himself]

10:02.233 --> 10:03.935
[door closes]

10:04.035 --> 10:05.016
Mr. Quinn?

10:05.116 --> 10:06.497
Nola? [chuckles]
Hey, sweetie.

10:06.597 --> 10:07.778
How are you?

10:07.878 --> 10:09.940
Um...

10:10.040 --> 10:11.702
I have to talk to you.

10:11.802 --> 10:13.804
What's up, kiddo?

10:16.046 --> 10:18.027
This, um... this morning,

10:18.128 --> 10:19.309
I went by
Mrs. Quinn's office

10:19.409 --> 10:22.792
to pick up my paycheck,

10:22.892 --> 10:26.615
and I overheard her
talking with Chief Pratt.

10:29.058 --> 10:31.200
Take a look at that.

10:31.300 --> 10:34.122
[Pratt reading]:
"Nola, my darling,

10:34.222 --> 10:38.326
were you to die,
where would my love go?

10:38.426 --> 10:41.329
To lose you is to lose
every part of me,

10:41.429 --> 10:45.853
for I have secretly
bequeathed to you

10:45.953 --> 10:49.777
all that I am..."

10:49.877 --> 10:51.138
[Tamara]:
See, he's a criminal

10:51.238 --> 10:52.379
and a sexual predator.

10:52.479 --> 10:54.981
Now, what are you
gonna do about it?

10:55.081 --> 10:57.143
Well, I can't do
anything right away.

10:57.243 --> 10:59.025
Why the hell not?

10:59.125 --> 11:02.148
You entered his house
illegally, Tamara.

11:02.248 --> 11:03.950
You stole his property.

11:04.050 --> 11:04.990
I could get in trouble

11:05.091 --> 11:06.872
just for having this
in my possession.

11:06.972 --> 11:09.595
Then what do you
suggest we do?

11:09.695 --> 11:11.797
Keep it
in your safe for now.

11:11.897 --> 11:13.038
And don't worry,

11:13.138 --> 11:15.040
you'll see how we deal
with guys like that

11:15.140 --> 11:17.142
around here.

11:19.384 --> 11:22.366
Okay, and...?

11:22.466 --> 11:23.568
Oh...

11:23.668 --> 11:27.211
I need you to get
that note, Mr. Quinn.

11:27.311 --> 11:29.053
I beg you to get
that note, please,

11:29.153 --> 11:31.255
or Harry will
go to jail, and...

11:31.355 --> 11:32.576
it'll be all my fault.

11:32.676 --> 11:34.257
I-I-I'm sorry,
Nola, I don't--

11:34.357 --> 11:35.258
He only wrote that note

11:35.358 --> 11:36.299
because I tried
to kill myself.

11:36.399 --> 11:37.781
It's all my fault.

11:37.881 --> 11:40.183
I'm sorry, Nola, I don't...
I don't... I...

11:40.283 --> 11:42.064
Mr. Quinn,

11:42.165 --> 11:44.026
please, I'm begging you.

11:44.126 --> 11:45.708
Please help me.

11:45.808 --> 11:47.469
Please help us,
do you understand?

11:47.569 --> 11:50.192
I can't do
what you're asking me to.

11:50.292 --> 11:52.114
I can't... condone

11:52.214 --> 11:53.515
whatever's going on
between the two of you.

11:53.615 --> 11:54.436
I-I...

11:54.536 --> 11:56.718
For the love of God?

11:56.818 --> 11:59.981
I don't think God would
approve of it either.

12:01.783 --> 12:04.445
We love each other
like no one's ever loved.

12:04.545 --> 12:06.527
Look at me.

12:06.627 --> 12:09.249
Our love is pure,
and it's beautiful,

12:09.349 --> 12:11.011
and I would do anything for him.

12:11.111 --> 12:13.093
Anything, do you understand?

12:13.193 --> 12:14.134
If I lose him, Mr. Quinn,

12:14.234 --> 12:16.816
it's like losing
a part of myself...

12:16.916 --> 12:21.140
the best part of myself.

12:21.240 --> 12:23.242
I'll never find anyone
like him again.

12:26.725 --> 12:27.866
I don't know what to say, Nola.

12:27.967 --> 12:29.748
You know what it feels like,
Mr. Quinn.

12:29.848 --> 12:32.130
Love?

12:34.332 --> 12:35.473
When you know--

12:35.573 --> 12:36.715
Maybe we should go
in the house

12:36.815 --> 12:38.436
and have a hot chocolate
or something.

12:38.536 --> 12:40.158
No, Mr. Quinn, we can't just
go and have a hot chocolate.

12:40.258 --> 12:41.279
Just relax.

12:41.379 --> 12:42.680
Are you listening to me,
Mr. Quinn?

12:42.780 --> 12:43.761
I am, but, you know,

12:43.861 --> 12:44.962
you're just going
through something now.

12:45.062 --> 12:46.043
You need to relax--

12:46.143 --> 12:47.965
Am I going through something?

12:48.065 --> 12:50.447
I need him to stay alive,
Mr. Quinn,

12:50.547 --> 12:51.768
so can you just please
listen to me?

12:51.868 --> 12:53.870
Are you gonna
get that note for me?

12:58.394 --> 12:59.335
I-I can't, I can't.

12:59.435 --> 13:01.577
I...

13:01.677 --> 13:03.679
I'm sorry, Nola.

13:10.646 --> 13:14.209
<i>[Quinn]: It was incredible,</i>
<i>her passion and intensity...</i>

13:15.370 --> 13:18.313
And I envied her.

13:18.413 --> 13:20.675
What she felt for Harry

13:20.775 --> 13:22.777
was something I had never felt
for anyone myself.

13:24.018 --> 13:26.320
And that's
when I realized

13:26.420 --> 13:29.423
I had probably
never been in love.

13:31.825 --> 13:34.167
I asked her what she intended
to do about Chief Pratt,

13:34.267 --> 13:35.288
since he knew about the note.

13:35.388 --> 13:36.169
Right.

13:36.269 --> 13:37.210
