13:37.310 --> 13:38.211
Hmm?

13:38.311 --> 13:40.173
Come in?

13:40.273 --> 13:41.334
Oh.

13:41.434 --> 13:44.417
Well, hello, Nola.

13:44.517 --> 13:46.178
What's going on?

13:46.278 --> 13:48.340
