14:53.059 --> 14:54.841
Screw you, Tamara!

14:54.941 --> 14:56.603
Making up some story
I got cancer

14:56.703 --> 14:59.165
'cause your party sucks!

14:59.265 --> 15:01.447
Screw you and your gossip,
and your meddling,

15:01.547 --> 15:03.369
your, "Oh, don't touch me,
I'm too tired.

