She was punishing
herself,

47:45.907 --> 47:47.409
whipping herself,

47:47.509 --> 47:51.072
plunging her head
into a bath of icy water.

47:53.674 --> 47:55.676
Well...

47:57.678 --> 48:00.821
that poor little girl,

